#: metabrainz/templates/payments/donate.html:3
#: metabrainz/templates/payments/donate.html:7
msgid "Make a Donation"
msgstr "寄付を行う"

#: metabrainz/templates/payments/donate.html:10
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If you feel that our projects are a worthwhile effort, please consider "
"contributing money to the\n"
"      MetaBrainz Foundation, which is a <a "
"href=\"%(wikipedia_non_profit_url)s\">\n"
"      501(c)(3) tax-exempt non-profit</a> based in California. All of "
"your donations will be tax-deductible\n"
"      and you will receive a receipt that you can use to deduct your "
"donation off your taxes if you are a\n"
"      US taxpayer."
msgstr ""
"私たちのプロジェクトが価値ある取り組みであるとお考えでしたら、\n"
"カリフォルニア州に拠点を置く、<a href=\"%(wikipedia_non_profit_url)s\"> 501(c)(3) "
"免税非営利団体</a>である\n"
"MetaBrainz Foundationへの寄付をご検討ください。\n"
"ご寄付の全額は税額控除の対象となり、米国納税者の方には、\n"
"税額控除に利用できる領収書をお送りいたします。"

#: metabrainz/templates/payments/donate.html:18
msgid ""
"Your donations will be used to operate projects of the MetaBrainz "
"Foundation. This includes paying\n"
"      for ongoing expenses like hosting, hardware, maintaining a modest "
"office, and paying a minimal\n"
"      salary for MetaBrainz employees."
msgstr ""
"皆様からの寄付金は、MetaBrainz財団のプロジェクト運営に充てられます。これには、\n"
"継続的な経費が含まれ、ホスティングやハードウェア費用、小規模なオフィスの維持費、\n"
"およびMetaBrainzの従業員への最低限の給与の支払いが該当します。"

#: metabrainz/templates/payments/donate.html:23
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Where has my contribution gone? See our <a "
"href=\"%(finance_reports_url)s\">transparent finances</a>."
msgstr ""
"私の寄付金はどこへ行ったのでしょうか？当財団の<a "
"href=\"%(finance_reports_url)s\">透明性の高い財務状況</a>をご覧ください。"

#: metabrainz/templates/payments/donate.html:24
